request.description:
Get current authenticated user information

**Response Example:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "user": {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "Director Name",
    "email": "director@university.edu",
    "role": "director"
  }
}
```

**Access**: Manager Only

**Request Body**:
```json
{
  "team_name": "Team Name",
  "company_name": "Company Name",
  "credentials": {
    "email": "team@domain.com",
    "password": "securepassword"
  }
}
```

